cn.ficos.Compiler.Syntax

接口 MangoListener

  • 所有超级接口:
    org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
    所有已知实现类:
    ClassCollector, Field_FunctionCollector, MangoBaseListener

    public interface MangoListener
extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
    This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by MangoParser.
